{"tid":1879582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民豬咀不是夢]《柳葉刀》:  普通口罩作用不大，治癒者仍可播毒","createTime":"2020-02-14T09:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T10:54:41.000Z","uid":31539,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"58927e6d9c0c043b896dd436e12b8753ef9b26c9","tid":1879582,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:30:42.000Z","msg":"原文link <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lanres/article/PIIS2213-2600(20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flanres%2Farticle%2FPIIS2213-2600%2820&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=fee60bf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lanres/article/PIIS2213-2600(20</a>)30066-7/fulltext<br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n1.Recent evidence suggests that even someone who is non-symptomatic can spread COVID-19 with high efficiency, and conventional measures of protection such as face masks, provide insufficient protection。<br />\n<br />\n2.This recent case shows that not only can subclinical patients transmit the virus effectively but patients can also shed high amounts of the virus and infect others even after recovery from the acute illness.<br />\n<br />\n講明武肺傳染力太勁，冇病徵都夠做毒王<br />\n大家都係咪咁迷信普通口罩<br />\n少d出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6cff88cbb05370040ee760ec0452900e4bb43d","tid":1879582,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"btw連支那醫生都叫齊ppe先掂<br />\n仲返緊工d醫護自己諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThese findings warrant aggressive measures (such as N95 masks, goggles, and protective gowns) to ensure the safety of health-care workers during this COVID-19 outbreak"},{"pid":"78fa1679ae8e4f90b4cebc341996934d058bec4